            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link">
              <h3>Quranic Studies</h3>
            </a>
            <p>Participate in our Quranic study sessions, where we delve deep into the teachings of the Quran. Classes are available for all age groups.</p>
          </div>
        </div><!-- End Service Item -->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="service-item position-relative">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link">
              <h3>Community Services</h3>
            </a>
            <p>We offer various community services including food distribution, charity drives, and support for the needy. Get involved and make a difference.</p>
          </div>
        </div><!-- End Service Item -->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
          <div class="service-item position-relative">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-child"></i>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link">
              <h3>Youth Engagement</h3>
            </a>
            <p>Our youth programs are designed to engage and inspire the younger members of our community through educational and recreational activities.</p>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link"></a>
          </div>
        </div><!-- End Service Item -->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
          <div class="service-item position-relative">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-book"></i>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link">
              <h3>Library</h3>
            </a>
            <p>Explore our extensive collection of Islamic books, journals, and digital resources. Our library is open to all members of the community for study and research.</p>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link"></a>
          </div>
        </div><!-- End Service Item -->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
          <div class="service-item position-relative">
            <div class="icon">
              <i class="fas fa-microphone-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link">
              <h3>Islamic Lectures</h3>
            </a>
            <p>Attend our regular lectures on various Islamic topics, delivered by knowledgeable scholars. Enhance your understanding of Islam and its teachings.</p>
            <a href="#" class="stretched-link"></a>
          </div>
        </div><!-- End Service Item -->

      </div>

    </div>

  </section><!-- /Services Section -->


